# Slangy environment variables
#
# The AI conversation tutor uses Google Gemini 2.5 Flash.
# Get a key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey and put it here.
# Without a key, the tutor runs in a built-in simulated "practice mode" so the app
# still works end to end.

GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model id (defaults to gemini-2.5-flash)
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
